title: Florida- 1b/1bath 55 Building Month Not Available until December
posting_body: ['Hello, I have a 2 bedroom 2 bathroom Condo at Poinciana Place 3465 Via Poinciana Place on the 4 floor.', 'This is a turn key Condo, It has everything, just bring your clothes..', 'I am from Ireland and I am going home to care for my Mom in December..', 'This is a 55 Plus building !!', 'You must be over 55 years..', 'You must be over 55 to live here $3,000.00 a Month Includes Electric/Cable/internet/water/garbage/condo dues.', 'You will have no Extra bills !!', 'I would like to meet you in Person before I rent to you..', 'I am a Travel Nurse and at present I am working in Delaware until November, we can Skype or face time.', 'I will also do A extensive background check on you !!!', 'I am very clean and house proud and will only rent to the SAME..!!!', 'Please look at this area and the community on there website..', 'I also have a Yellow FJ cruiser and I will rent my car out also if your interested..', 'No PETS allowed at this building..', 'This is a 55 plus building, You must be over 55..!!!!!', 'Please E-mail me and in order to know your not a scam start the e-mail with the word --Ireland---', "Without- Ireland- I won't respond..", 'Keep in Mind this condo is not available until January 1st..', 'I also will be renting out my Yellow FJ Cruiser if you need a car as I wont need it when I am in Ireland..', 'I also have a home in Traverse City..']
